{"tid":1277505,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林 鄭 月 娥 哀 悼 鬥 委 會 主 任 楊 光 逝 世","createTime":"2019-07-02T08:02:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T07:34:10.000Z","uid":36238,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3246da655208055b28680e126946bb23065c7197","tid":1277505,"uid":36238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T08:02:25.000Z","msg":"署理行政長官<strong>林鄭月娥</strong>今日對香港工會聯合會前會長楊光逝世，表示哀悼，並代表政府向其家人致以深切慰問。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥指楊光多年來積極參與香港工運，對勞工福利有突出建樹，長期為廣大基層服務，並於2001年獲頒授大紫荊勳章。<br />\n<br />\n勞工及福利局局長<strong>張建宗</strong>也對楊光逝世深表哀悼，指楊光在任期間致力維護和促進勞工和基層權益，貢獻良多。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.news.gov.hk/tc/categories/school_work/html/2015/05/20150516_182233.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fcategories%2Fschool_work%2Fhtml%2F2015%2F05%2F20150516_182233.shtml&d=Mrz8gheyF4cbCiJyPb%2FME8ZiPQ%2BZ2BAZCV%2B6nVsqWzo%3D&h=98512dd2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.news.gov.hk/tc/categories/school_work/html/2015/05/20150516_182233.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e69278389e507cad5a4302249d5b227eee999fc8","tid":1277505,"uid":35081,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T08:03:39.000Z","msg":"2015年05月16日"},{"pid":"ac7275554a08497bbb34b20ee898ac9ccfd70d22","tid":1277505,"uid":193642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T08:04:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f19a193bd24ff3d6c1d1f6cf9745b4e8682b0066","tid":1277505,"uid":894,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T08:04:32.000Z","msg":"真暴徒<img src=\